    "ML models trained on large datasets of malware samples can detect new and evolving threats, enabling organizations to develop proactive defense strategies and enhance their resilience against malware attacks.Christodorescu et al. [7] emphasize the effectiveness of ML-based malware classifiers in detecting and mitigating malware infections across diverse IT environments.",
